descriptionHtml:
This is a RaceMenu Preset of my self confident HighElf, called Ignis.
Maybe, I can make someone out there happy with this.

[b]Mods I use for him:[/b]

Body: [url=https://www.loverslab.com/files/file/498-sos-schlongs-of-skyrim/]SoS [/url] with [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26145]Smooth Body Textures for Better Males and SoS[/url]
Face: [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/27815]Fine Face Textures for Men[/url]

Hair: [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311]KS Hairdo's - Renewal[/url] -> for the strong haircolor I added this mod [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/88254]Smooth Silky Straight KS Hairdo's Retexture[/url]
Brows: [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411]Brows[/url]
Eyes: [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/74948]Lind's Elven Eyes[/url]


[b]Armor I used for the screenshots: [/b]

Regal Huntsman Armor (DreamBurrow)

Follower version is now available (separate mod).


Hope you like him! :)
author: Thrwomp
